                h3.l-sect Brief
                p.ml-sect
                    |For a senior design course, our team was tasked with seeking a local organization whose values we shared; conducting user research to identify problems, which we then solved through UX & service design. 
                    |We were fortunate to be able to work with Arc'teryx's Kitsilano and Metrotown branches,  and the post-sales team from Arc'teryx HQ.

       
                figure.ml-sect   
                    img(data-src="imgs/arcy/kits.jpg" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 3 2'%3E%3C/svg%3E" ).lazy        
