                    //- figcaption Meeting at Arc'teryx Kitsilano branch, the outdoors customer-focused flagship.
                p.ml-sect Arc'teryx is an international design-driven high-end outdoor clothing & gear brand based in Vancouver. The brand is committed to its goals of sustainability through its manufacturing as well as its durability-focused design and extensive repair policy.
            
