                p.ml-sect To attain a nuanced understanding of Arc’teryx customers, 
                    mark we conducted 8 qualitative interviews seeking to understand motivations, behaviors, and rituals. 
                    |These included outdoor enthusiasts, urban commuters, techwear fans, and casual shoppers. 
                figure.mlmr-sect
